            <div type="translation">
                <p>Brothers, glory and honor and peace to every man who works good. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Badly damaged. Very fragmentary. The words τιμή, εἰρήνη, ἐργαζομένῳ are misspelled. Accents and breathings with errors. The verse is taken from the Rom. 2:10.
</p>
